    AP -->|Registration, login, application data,\nrequirements, photo, profile updates| SYS
    SYS -->|Account status, application status,\nnotifications, announcements| AP

    AS -->|Period setup, requirements setup,\nstatus updates, disbursement actions,\nannouncements, SMS broadcast| SYS
    SYS -->|Dashboards, logs, reports,\nsearch results, exports| AS

    SYS -->|Outbound SMS payload| SG
    SG -->|Delivery response / status| SYS

